1
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:56,160
This used to be my happy home.

2
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:58,640
Thanks to your brother, Song Huainan,

3
00:00:58,640 --> 00:01:00,200
everything is in ruins.

4
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:21,090
Do you think you really know Song Huainan?

5
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:26,720
Song Huainan is violent and suspicious by nature.

6
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:29,120
After I go back,

7
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:32,600
I'm afraid he won't even tolerate you.

8
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:07,920
Singing.

9
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,160
At a time like this,

10
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:10,960
you still have the mood for that?

11
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,160
About the factory.

12
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,560
Isn't everything ready?

13
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:19,600
The first batch of samples will be produced soon.

14
00:02:23,079 --> 00:02:24,400
Where are you going?

15
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:29,420
I'm going to find Shengsheng.

16
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,480
Song Huainan,

17
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,800
how could you lock Shengsheng up?

18
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,960
I just want her to get some rest.

19
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,840
She took a bullet for you.

20
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:48,560
Move.

21
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:49,640
Huainan.

22
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,840
Are you so impatient

23
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,120
talking to me now?

24
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,440
Don't you care about

25
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:56,800
our past bond at all?

26
00:02:58,640 --> 00:03:00,000
Our past bond?

27
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,320
What bond?

28
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:05,160
I was just curious how a man

29
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:06,360
could be so beautiful.

30
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,820
I just teased you a little.

31
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:10,120
Who am I? Song Huainan.

32
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:12,420
Why would I do such despicable things

33
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:14,840
with an actor like you?

34
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,000
Yao Lifu.

35
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:19,760
I'm warning you.

36
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,880
If you dare ruin my reputation again,

37
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:25,160
I'll make the Yao family pay.

38
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:27,240
Become the next Zhu family.

39
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,760
All right, you may leave.

40
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:39,600
No need to guard Madam anymore.

41
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:40,530
Yes, Commander.

42
00:03:46,160 --> 00:03:46,960
Go and find out

43
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:48,960
where Song Qingzhou went last night.

44
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,480
Also,

45
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:51,360
check if Madam left the house.

46
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:52,800
Go now.

47
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:53,720
Yes, sir.

48
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:09,160
What are you doing?

49
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,930
I'm willing to help you.

50
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:15,160
Tell me.

51
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,740
What do I need to do?

52
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:24,200
I want to get into the Yao family's factory.

53
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:27,250
What does this have to do with the factory?

54
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:35,120
This is the real secret formula for the Zhu family's medicinal soap.

55
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,680
The formula Song Huainan gave the Yao family was fake.

56
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:44,280
Soap made from that

57
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,860
won't pass the foreigners' inspection.

58
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:49,800
I need you to help me find some herbs.

59
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,000
Without those herbs.

60
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:53,640
It is impossible to make the real Zhu's Medicinal Soap.

61
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:56,240
You want to take the herbs into the Yao factory?

62
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:56,960
Yes.

63
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,200
Why?

64
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:01,340
I'm going to help the Yaos.

65
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,440
It's so early.

66
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:19,040
What are you doing at my house?

67
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:21,570
What were you doing with Shengsheng just now?

68
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,460
What else could I be doing?

69
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,800
Shengsheng hasn't recovered yet.

70
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:29,130
Of course I was checking on her condition.

71
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,440
It's not convenient to talk here.

72
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,170
Come with me.

73
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:44,610
What exactly do you want to say?

74
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:47,570
If Shengsheng had listened to me back then

75
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,640
and married you,

76
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:52,320
perhaps things would be different.

77
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:56,800
You mean

78
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:59,640
you wanted your sister to marry me back then?

79
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:01,280
Song Huainan is a tyrant.

80
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,680
Shengsheng won't be happy with him.

81
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:06,920
Qingzhou.

82
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,810
I only have this one sister.

83
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:11,920
Can you take good care of her for me?

84
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:14,180
Don't let anyone bully her again.

85
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:17,600
You don't need to tell me that.

86
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,800
I'll keep her safe.

87
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:36,530
Shopkeeper,

88
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,300
I need these herbs.

89
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,200
Okay.

90
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:00,600
Qingzhou,

91
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:04,120
this is your favorite egg noodle soup from when you were little.

92
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:04,920
Go on, try it.

93
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,970
See if it still tastes the same.

94
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:08,820
Thank you, Mother.

95
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,240
Qingzhou,

96
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,490
you've got something on your mind.

97
00:07:25,080 --> 00:07:25,880
It's nothing.

98
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:31,200
You've been distracted since you came in.

99
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,130
What exactly happened?

100
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,720
Tell me.

101
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:37,080
See if I can help.

102
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:47,040
Mother.

103
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:51,560
You have suffered too much all these years.

104
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,560
Don't worry.

105
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,800
I won't let you suffer in vain.

106
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:58,280
I will definitely seek justice from Song Huainan.

107
00:07:58,280 --> 00:07:59,960
Qingzhou, what are you planning to do?

108
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:00,420
Mother.

109
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,160
Mother.

110
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,320
Song Huainan is powerful.

111
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,040
You are all alone.

112
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:09,640
How can you fight him?

113
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,120
I know you hate him.

114
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,960
But you must understand.

115
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:13,840
Revenge

116
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,760
cannot be achieved through impulse.

117
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:18,660
Mother.

118
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:20,400
Rest assured.

119
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:23,320
I will plan carefully and act with caution.

120
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:25,320
Mother.

121
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:38,960
Mother.

122
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:41,559
This is what I've saved over the years.

123
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:42,890
It's everything I have.

124
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:43,799
Take this.

125
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:50,440
Mother.

126
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:00,640
Mother.

127
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,480
All these years,

128
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:04,720
it's been hard on you.

129
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:08,920
By the way,

130
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,800
Song Huainan is ruthless.

131
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:12,280
He will surely come after you.

132
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,600
You must watch out for him.

133
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,160
Mother,

134
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:15,490
don't worry.

135
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:16,840
I know.

136
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,700
Song Qingzhou.

137
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:35,220
What were you doing this morning?

138
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:38,320
Nothing. Just wandering around.

139
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,080
Why did you cut your hair?

140
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:41,560
Why?

141
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:44,440
Do I need your permission to cut my hair?

142
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,440
Song Huainan.

143
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:02,080
For how you hurt my mother,

144
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:05,480
I'll make you pay a hundredfold.
